<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Art Gallery</title>

    <!-- Your Custom CSS Styles -->
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        h2 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .gallery {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .artwork {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 300px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .artwork img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }

        .buy-button {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 20px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.3s ease-in-out;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: 10px; /* Added margin-top for space */
            border-radius: 15px; /* Added rounded corners */
        }

        .artwork:hover .buy-button {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        .artwork:hover img {
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }

        h3 {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        p {
            color: #555;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h2>Explore these captivating artworks by talented artists.</h2>

    <div class="gallery">
        <div class="artwork">
            <img src="./images/img1.jpg" alt="Children and Bicycle">
            <h3>Children and Bicycle</h3>
            <p>Artist: Sarah Johnson</p>
            <p>An enchanting portrayal of childhood innocence and joy, where a group of children explores the world on their bicycles.</p>
            <button class="buy-button">Buy</button>
        </div>

        <div class="artwork">
            <img src="./images/img2.jpg" alt="The Golden Era" style="width: 600px;">
            <h3>The Golden Era</h3>
            <p>Artist: Michael Rodriguez</p>
            <p>A mesmerizing depiction of a bygone era, bathed in the warm hues of nostalgia, capturing the essence of a golden age.</p>
            <button class="buy-button">Buy</button>
        </div>

        <div class="artwork">
            <img src="./images/img3.jpg" alt="Color Splash" style="width: 600px;">
            <h3>Color Splash</h3>
            <p>Artist: Emily Chen</p>
            <p>An explosion of vibrant colors that dance and mingle, creating a captivating visual symphony that celebrates the beauty of diversity.</p>
            <button class="buy-button">Buy</button>
        </div>

        <div class="artwork">
            <img src="./images/img4.jpg" alt="The Girl">
            <h3>The Girl</h3>
            <p>Artist: Christopher Anderson</p>
            <p>A poignant portrayal of a girl whose eyes tell a thousand stories, inviting viewers to ponder the depth of human experience.</p>
            <button class="buy-button">Buy</button>
        </div>

        <div class="artwork">
            <img src="./images/img5.jpg" alt="CountrySide">
            <h3>CountrySide</h3>
            <p>Artist: Maria Sanchez</p>
            <p>A serene landscape capturing the tranquility of the countryside, where nature's beauty unfolds in every rolling hill and rustling leaf.</p>
            <button class="buy-button">Buy</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
